Subject: A0775-APP2356-S: The transaction log for database 'tempdb' is full due to 'ACTIVE_TRANSACTION'.
Description:
A0775-APP2356-S: The following error message is showing in job: 
7.AEM_DirectACLs_LCycle_FollowUp_Owners:
The transaction log for database 'tempdb' is full due to 'ACTIVE_TRANSACTION'.

We have also received notification that the F: is low on space.

Please advise how we can resolve these issues.

Thank you,
Alison.
DevOps_Steps_to_Reproduce__c: Run any job or report on an overfilled DB
What_We_Know__c: Simple Recovery Mode, transaction log bloated
Next_Steps__c: Waiting for the result of analytics queries
Solution_Comment__c: We advised you to contact your DBA Team and preform a manual cleanup. You have confirmed that everything is working as intended now.
